{"tid":1437882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放棄啦，香港最緊要繁榮穩定，自由法治放埋一邊先啦","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:58:24.000Z","uid":293292,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a8cfbba962eb796dcc7f02d18f0b56ef04d6e72a","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n香港今日既經濟繁除左係過去幾代人既成果之外，<br />\n更重要既係建基於一個有<span style=\"color: red;\">法治，自由既社會，令外商有信心投資。</span><br />\n抗爭者堅持上街絕對唔係要損害香港，一個我地視為屋企既地方。<br />\n但眼見香港禮樂崩壞，法治淪喪，自由日漸收緊，特別係六月以黎政府對民意既篾視，警察既濫權，我地無辨法唔繼續企出黎，守護香港既核心價值。<br />\n雖然短期內經濟有機會受影(一定比唔上外圍因素)，但我相信呢D核心價值先可以確保香港長遠既經濟發展。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民字"},{"pid":"c8970e3e4010eb524b30a202a96b785e53dd248e","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a8064873714885f28a554c7f3f42eedca4505168","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e6a7f796bca8fdb5e657ebb9951c93890bf48965","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:40.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ecef13a33098bd87fc661d419ce1563fa32dc25b","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d2ad07845d2cee23a0feae37ae7072ee4c0e877f","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d85a466c20af949f5b373025a6ba073c59fab5a5","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c9cd9536e2896297e01ea5b249dd5abf35740221","tid":1437882,"uid":293292,"like":0